      <title>快乐蜂调查涉嫌影响数百万人的数据泄露事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/jollibee-investigates-alleged-data-breach-affecting-millions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾最大的餐厅运营商快乐蜂食品公司 (Jollibee Foods Corp.) 正在调查一起可能影响其数百万顾客的数据泄露事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/jollibee-investigates-alleged-data-breach-affecting-millions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 05:56:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
